OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy at
OL,6,Ftimes, with some isolated showers at
OL,7,Ffirst, these clearing during the early
OL,8,Fhours. Some clear spells developing,
OL,9,Fwhere these occur, there is a chance
OL,10,Fof fog patches before dawn. Winds
OL,11,Fgenerally light, though breezy along
OL,12,Fthe coast.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FSome occasional bright spells
OL,15,Fand scattered heavy showers developing
OL,16,Fduring the afternoon, with a chance of
OL,17,Fthunder. Low cloud increasing
OL,18,Fovernight. Temperatures slightly
OL,19,Fcooler than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
